<subSubSection id="C370650EFFDDFFCBFF29FA2DBDFAC925" pageId="14" pageNumber="235" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8BD53685FFDDFFCBFF29FA2DBDFAC925" blockId="14.[136,1452,1472,2075]" pageId="14" pageNumber="235">
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFDDFFCBFF29FA2DBE30CADC" bold="true" box="[136,261,1472,1498]" pageId="14" pageNumber="235">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
—This species is characterized by the relatively small-sized teliospores among species having spermogonia and aecia on 
<taxonomicName id="4C6A4D06FFDDFFCBFE82FA09BE54CAF8" box="[291,353,1508,1534]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Grossulariaceae" genus="Ribes" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="14" pageNumber="235" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFDDFFCBFE82FA09BE54CAF8" box="[291,353,1508,1534]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="235">Ribes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. It is also phylogenetically close to 
<taxonomicName id="4C6A4D06FFDDFFCBFCA4FA08BC8CCAF9" authority="DC." authorityName="DC." box="[773,953,1509,1535]" class="Pucciniomycetes" family="Pucciniaceae" genus="Puccinia" kingdom="Fungi" order="Pucciniales" pageId="14" pageNumber="235" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="caricina">
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFDDFFCBFCA4FA08BCB5CAF8" box="[773,896,1509,1534]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="235">P. caricina</emphasis>
DC.
</taxonomicName>
on 
<taxonomicName id="4C6A4D06FFDDFFCBFC46FA09BB10CAF8" box="[999,1061,1508,1534]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Grossulariaceae" genus="Ribes" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="14" pageNumber="235" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFDDFFCBFC46FA09BB10CAF8" box="[999,1061,1508,1534]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="235">Ribes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(sometimes reported as 
<taxonomicName id="4C6A4D06FFDDFFCBFAE0FA08BFD6C925" authority="Rebent." authorityName="Rebent." class="Pucciniomycetes" family="Pucciniaceae" genus="Puccinia" kingdom="Fungi" order="Pucciniales" pageId="14" pageNumber="235" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="caricis">
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFDDFFCBFAE0FA08BA9ECAF8" box="[1345,1451,1509,1534]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="235">P. caricis</emphasis>
Rebent.
</taxonomicName>
), but has a distinct lineage from 
<taxonomicName id="4C6A4D06FFDDFFCBFDEEF9E4BDF2C924" box="[591,711,1545,1570]" class="Pucciniomycetes" family="Pucciniaceae" genus="Puccinia" kingdom="Fungi" order="Pucciniales" pageId="14" pageNumber="235" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="caricina">
<emphasis id="B91EEA97FFDDFFCBFDEEF9E4BDF2C924" box="[591,711,1545,1570]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="235">P. caricina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
